Code preview of 企业主体表sl_company_main

drop table if exists sl_company_main;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_company_main */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_company_main
(
companyMainId bigint(20) not null auto_increment,
corName varchar(250) character set utf8 not null comment '企业名称',
simpleName varchar(100) character set utf8 comment '企业简称',
lawName varchar(50) character set utf8 not null comment '法人姓名',
organizeCode varchar(100) character set utf8 not null comment '组织机构代码',
businessCode varchar(100) character set utf8 comment '营业执照号码',
haveCharcter smallint(6) comment '所有性制性质',
tax varchar(50) character set utf8 comment '传真',
tel varchar(50) character set utf8 not null comment '联系电话',
mail varchar(50) character set utf8 comment '邮箱地址',
messageAddress varchar(250) character set utf8 comment '通讯地址',
primary key (companyMainId)
);

alter table sl_company_main comment '企业主体表';
